00:17:34,569 --> 00:17:37,709
Aku kehilangan kuncinya.

243
00:17:39,380 --> 00:17:40,780
Apakah kami bisa membelinya

244
00:17:42,209 --> 00:17:44,349
di mesin penjual?

245
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,250
Karena dia harus pergi bekerja.

246
00:17:52,990 --> 00:17:54,130
Astaga.

247
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:07,839
- Yang ini?
- Benar.

248
00:18:10,179 --> 00:18:11,339
Terima kasih.

249
00:18:11,709 --> 00:18:14,179
Terima kasih banyak.

250
00:18:14,179 --> 00:18:16,109
- Tentu.
