251
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,079
Sampai jumpa.

252
00:18:23,219 --> 00:18:24,459
Ada-ada saja.

253
00:18:29,530 --> 00:18:30,599
Bisa?

254
00:18:35,030 --> 00:18:36,099
Ini.

255
00:18:36,599 --> 00:18:40,069
Ambillah. Jangan sampai hilang.

256
00:18:40,540 --> 00:18:42,440
Simpan sampai kamu mati.

257
00:19:04,369 --> 00:19:05,880
Mau sarapan denganku?

258
